# Work Hours Follow — Design Kit

## Contents

```text
Design/
├── DESIGN_SYSTEM.md
├── SCREEN_SPECS.md
├── COMPONENTS.md
├── IMPLEMENTATION_NOTES.md
├── UI_GUIDELINES.md
└── References/
    ├── Design_Board.png
    ├── 01_Overview.png
    ├── 02_Entries.png
    ├── 03_Add_Edit_Entry.png
    ├── 04_History.png
    ├── 05_Settings.png
    ├── 06_Components.png
    ├── 07_Tokens_Typography.png
    └── 08_Layout_Icons.png
```

Place this folder in the repository as:

```text
Docs/Design/
```

Recommended root documents:

```text
PROJECT_DESCRIPTION.md
RULES.md
Docs/Design/
```

Codex should read the project description, project rules, design system, relevant screen specification, and matching image before implementing each screen.
